I've been trying to upload large files to S3 using the multi-part uploading in the Unity S3 package.  It works well enough, but it allocates memory the size of the whole file and never frees it.  I've tried using the FilePath member and specifying InputStream but both methods leak memory.  Below is some simple code to demonstrate the issue.  It uploads 8MB chunks.  Task Manager can be used to monitor memory.  Memory usage will just increase forever while the app is running.  Tested in Unity 5.3.7 and 5.5.1.

